14. Overfitting and Underfitting

14.1 Overfitting

Definition:
Model memorizes training data and performs poorly on new data.

Solution:
- More Data
- Regularization
- Cross Validation

14.2 Underfitting

Definition:
Model fails to learn important patterns.

Solution:
- Better Features
- Complex Models

